review: I'm 65 year old. I visited Dr. Gayathri Chinmayee for my teeth and gum related problems. I had severe bleeding and pus discharge from gums. Also multiple teeth decays. After a multiple visits to various dentists with no benefit on the treatments, I finally found this doctor and very glad that she has done the right diagnosis and explained me about all the treatment options. very gentle during the treatments and I found a significant change in my oral condition. Can't thank her enough. thank-you doctor for being so kind to me. God bless you.

review: NeoDentistree is a place i would recommend anyone who wants to get their oral health care done with a doctor who values patients, their well being and their happiness. I had been to neodentistree for wisdom tooth extraction and Dr. Gayathri took care of it with ease. She explained in detail about the procedure, what and how it will be done and educates about the procedure well before the treatment. She has a lot of patience, is calm and listens to the patients worries. I can tell that you don't have to fear for pain during treatment as she is highly experienced and professional. I keep a smile after visiting Neodentistree. Would highly recommend this place for any treatments.
